	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-173138600" class="story-title"> <a   href="//slashdot.org/story/24/02/23/193230/staff-say-dells-return-to-office-mandate-is-a-stealth-layoff">Staff Say Dell's Return To Office Mandate is a Stealth Layoff</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.theregister.com/2024/02/20/dell_rto_mandate/"  title="External link - https://www.theregister.com/2024/02/20/dell_rto_mandate/" target="_blank"> (theregister.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
		<!--<span class="comments commentcnt-173138600" >55</span>-->
		

		
